videos.description: Michigan's Brandon Peters throws two touchdowns in the first half in addition to two rushing TDs from Chris Evans and Henry Poggi to head into the half up 28-0.  The Wolverines hold off the Terrapins in the second half for a 35-10 win.
videos.headline: Michigan cruises past Maryland
